Say '''Balasan''' et kumapat ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Iloilo]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 29,724 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 54.27 sq. km. Sikato et walad kumalima ya distrito. Say zip code to et 5018.	
															
